  "readme_html": "\n        \n          <p><img src=\"https://github.com/jmorganca/ollama/assets/251292/1867051c-434e-4873-a074-3fa7bc111423\" width=\"200\"/></p>\n\n<p>Solar is the first open-source 10.7 billion parameter language model. It\u2019s compact, yet remarkably powerful, and demonstrates state-of-the-art performance in models with parameters under 30B.</p>\n\n<p>This model leverages the Llama 2 architecture and employs the Depth Up-Scaling technique, integrating Mistral 7B weights into upscaled layers.</p>\n\n<p>On the H6 benchmark, this model outperforms models with up to 30B parameters, even the Mixtral 8X7B model.</p>\n\n<h2>References</h2>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/upstage/SOLAR-10.7B-Instruct-v1.0\" rel=\"nofollow\">HuggingFace</a></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.upstage.ai\" rel=\"nofollow\">Upstage AI</a></p>\n\n        \n      ",
